MPI with MPICH 


search for a file with  the expression:  #pragma omp parallel  
ex. OPFT.cc

< Some basic important parameters > 

at the beginning, 
reduction(+:PAbs, PScat) : specifies values that will be added for all threads. 

#pragma omp critical {}  : no two threads should run at the same time.  

Logging: commands to run a certain printf statement very occasionally, like 10 times in a loop that runs million times. 
ex) Homer's LogPercent routine. 


